text: Matjaž Kladnik (born 19 September 1975) is a Slovenian ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1994 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Slovenian male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Slovenia Category:Ski jumpers at the 1994 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Ljubljana
